description:
Let this special message from Lakewood's Grand Opening Weekend encourage you that you haven’t reached your limit. God wants to take you further than you’ve ever dreamed.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
